---
import ContentLayout from '../layouts/ContentLayout.astro';
---

<ContentLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy policy for Own Your Mind – what data we collect and how we use it."
  breadcrumbs={[{ label: 'Privacy Policy' }]}
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl">
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>

    <div class="prose">
      <p class="text-lg text-[var(--color-text-secondary)]">
        We keep this simple because our data collection is minimal. We don't run ads, we don't sell data,
        and we don't track you across the web.
      </p>

      <h2>What We Collect</h2>

      <h3>Website Analytics</h3>

      <p>
        This site is hosted on Cloudflare Pages. Cloudflare provides basic analytics (page views,
        visitor counts, countries) using server-side logging – no cookies, no tracking scripts, no
        fingerprinting. We use this to understand which content is useful. We cannot identify individual
        visitors from this data.
      </p>

      <h3>Newsletter</h3>

      <p>
        If you subscribe to our newsletter via Buttondown, we collect your email address. That's it.
        Your email is stored by <a href="https://buttondown.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Buttondown</a>
        and is used solely to send you our newsletter. You can unsubscribe at any time using the link
        in every email, and your data will be deleted.
      </p>

      <h3>Search</h3>

      <p>
        Site search is powered by Pagefind and runs entirely in your browser. No search queries are
        sent to any server.
      </p>

      <h2>What We Don't Collect</h2>

      <ul>
        <li>No cookies (beyond any set by Cloudflare for security/performance)</li>
        <li>No third-party tracking scripts</li>
        <li>No advertising pixels</li>
        <li>No personal data beyond newsletter sign-ups</li>
        <li>No user accounts or passwords</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>

      <p>We use the following third-party services:</p>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Cloudflare</strong> – hosting, CDN, and DNS. <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Their privacy policy</a>.</li>
        <li><strong>Buttondown</strong> – newsletter. <a href="https://buttondown.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Their privacy policy</a>.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Your Rights</h2>

      <p>
        Under the Australian Privacy Act 1988, you have the right to access and correct personal
        information we hold about you. If you're in the EU or UK, you also have rights under GDPR.
        In practice, the only personal data we might hold is your email address if you subscribed to
        the newsletter. To exercise these rights, contact us via
        <a href="https://x.com/0xBobski" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">@0xBobski on X</a>
        or unsubscribe directly from any newsletter email.
      </p>

      <h2>Changes</h2>

      <p>
        If we change this policy, we'll update it here. We won't start collecting data without telling you.
      </p>

      <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-text-tertiary)] mt-8">
        Last updated: March 2026
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</ContentLayout>
